â¤ï¸Adoptedâ¤ï¸Sharing again for this sweet senior!!! Capullo, #A3660692, is an 11 year old chihuahua/Jack Russell terrier mix who is having a hard time at the shelter. He is scared and confused in his kennel but once he gets out he transforms into an affectionate, happy, fun little guy. Who would guess he is a senior the way he zooms around the play yard? He loves attention, gets along with other small dogs and has the softest fur and the cutest underbite ever!! Capullo would love to find a quiet adult only home where he can be loved and adored for the amazing boy that he is! Please donâ€™t let him languish another day in his cold kennel.
